CustomProperties.Name: PrimaryOrange
CustomProperties.Tooltip: A custom property to set the primary color.

Rules.InvariantScript: LookUp('Tabs (Auto Responsive layout)'.TabItems, Tab_Name = 'Tabs (Auto Responsive layout)'.DefaultTab)
If('Tabs (Auto Responsive layout)'.Filled = true, ColorValue("#F3F3F3"), Color.White)
If('Tabs (Auto Responsive layout)'.Filled = true, If(ThisItem.IsSelected, Self.Fill, ColorValue("#E8E8E8")), RGBA(0,0,0,0))

If(ThisItem.IsSelected && 'Tabs (Auto Responsive layout)'.Filled = true, Color.White, If(ThisItem.IsSelected && 'Tabs (Auto Responsive layout)'.Filled = false, If('Tabs (Auto Responsive layout)'.PrimaryOrange = true, ColorValue("#D04A02"),ColorValue("#415385")),ColorValue("#696969")))
If(ThisItem.IsSelected && 'Tabs (Auto Responsive layout)'.Filled = true, If('Tabs (Auto Responsive layout)'.PrimaryOrange = true, ColorValue("#D04A02"), ColorValue("#415385")), RGBA(0,0,0,0))
If('Tabs (Auto Responsive layout)'.Filled = true, If(ThisItem.IsSelected, Self.Fill, ColorValue("#E8E8E8")), RGBA(0,0,0,0))

If(ThisItem.IsSelected && 'Tabs (Auto Responsive layout)'.Filled = true, Color.White, If(ThisItem.IsSelected && 'Tabs (Auto Responsive layout)'.Filled = false, If('Tabs (Auto Responsive layout)'.PrimaryOrange = true, ColorValue("#D04A02"),ColorValue("#415385")),ColorValue("#696969")))
If(ThisItem.IsSelected && 'Tabs (Auto Responsive layout)'.Filled = true, If('Tabs (Auto Responsive layout)'.PrimaryOrange = true, ColorValue("#D04A02"), ColorValue("#415385")), RGBA(0,0,0,0))
If(ThisItem.Tab_Name = Last('Tabs (Auto Responsive layout)'.TabItems).Tab_Name, Button4_4.Width+Button4_4.X , Parent.TemplateWidth - Self.X)
If(ThisItem.IsSelected, If('Tabs (Auto Responsive layout)'.PrimaryOrange = true, RGBA(208, 74, 2, 1), ColorValue("#415385")), RGBA(0, 0, 0, 0))
If('Tabs (Auto Responsive layout)'.Filled = true, false, ThisItem.IsSelected)
